      "content": "but why is resistance even a good thing? if the whole outcome is guaranteed to be nothingness, then all this \"rebellion\" is just prolonging the inevitable. it's like staying in a movie that you already know has a miserable ending just to prove a point to nobody. if nothing actually matters in the end, wouldn't the most logical, most peaceful thing to do be to just stop fighting it? to just opt out of the struggle entirely?",
